&lt;li&gt;18 vacation days, 9 company holidays, 5 sick days, and 2 personal days&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stock options for every full-time employee&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid parental leave&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401k benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commuter Benefits&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive health, dental, and vision insurance options&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
